<taxonomicNameLabel id="A22A57B4EEB23BD6FE39F8BAFD93F84F" box="[508,598,1908,1934]" pageId="483" pageNumber="484" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
, female. A, habitus, left; B, leg 5 and urosome, ventral; C, left caudal ramus, dorsal; D, posterolateral process of cephalic shield; E, rostrum; F, antennule; G, antenna; H, labrum; I, mandible; J, maxillule; K, maxilla. Scale bars: A, 0.1 mm; B, 0.05 mm; C–K, 0.02 mm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption id="DF126655EEB53BD1FF4DFA15FA6EFA37" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4591947" ID-Zenodo-Dep="4591947" box="[136,1451,1499,1526]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4591947/files/figure.png" pageId="484" pageNumber="485" startId="484.[136,239,1499,1525]" targetBox="[166,1398,203,1426]" targetPageId="484">
